Create a cscope database like this:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
cscope \-cbR
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04' 4.\h'+01'\c
